Package: wpgdata
Title: Access the Winnipeg Open Data Portal via OData V4
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Myo Minn", "Oo", , "dr.myominnoo@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4089-016X"))
Description: Query and download datasets from the City of Winnipeg Open Data 
    Portal (data.winnipeg.ca) using the OData V4 API. Provides a simple 
    interface to search, filter, and retrieve data with automatic pagination 
    support. Based on the Socrata OData V4 endpoint specification.
